    <body><p><span rend="main_text" rendition="div"><lb />
お<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">母</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">かあ</span><span type="rp">）</span></span><span type="ruby"><span type="rb">火</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">ひ</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>を<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">燃</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">も</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>すけえ。<lb />
そねえに<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">燃</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">も</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>さなくても<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">温</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">あたた</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>けえないか。<lb />
だって<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">今日</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">きょう</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>は<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">寒</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">さむ</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>いもの。<lb />
<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">寒</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">さむ</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>いか、そんだらくべろえ。<lb />
<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">明日</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">あす</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>、また<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">出</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">で</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>て<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">薪</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">たきぎ</span><span type="rp">）</span></span><span type="ruby"><span type="rb">取</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">と</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>ってくるわの<lb />
そう<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">心配</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">しんぱい</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>さっしゃんな。<lb />
<lb />
　　＊　＊　＊　＊　＊　＊<lb />
<lb />
お<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">母</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">かあ</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>、<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">燃</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">も</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>えたぜ<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">当</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">あ</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>たらっしゃい。<lb />
<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">汝</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">われ</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>、やかましいそげなもの<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">吹</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">ふ</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>くなよ。<lb />
ごじゅうからがたくさんきていたぜの、<lb />
あっちの<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">神社</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">おみや</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>の<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">森</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">もり</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>にきていたぜの、<lb />
ほら<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">鳴</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">な</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>いているだろの、<lb />
<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">俺</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">おら</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>のこの<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">笛</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">ふえ</span><span type="rp">）</span></span><span type="ruby"><span type="rb">聞</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">き</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>いて<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">鳴</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">な</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>いているだろの？<lb />
<span rend="sesame_dot" rendition="em">ふいふいふい</span><lb />
<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">悲</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">かな</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>しく<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">鳴</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">な</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>る<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">管笛</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">くだぶえ</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>。<lb />
<lb />
<lb />
<lb />
</span></p></body>
